oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (navy and yellow on white) announcing the 2018 Americana Honors and Awards hosted by the Milk Carton Kids and featuring Courtney Marie Andrews, Brandi Carlile, Rosanne Cash, Tyler Childers, Anderson East, Mary Gauthier, Buddy Guy, Lilly Hiatt, I'm With Her, Jason Isbell and the 400 Unit, Robert Earl Keen, k.d. lang, Nathaniel Rateliff and the Night Sweats, Lukas Nelson and Promise of the Real, Margo Price, John Prine, and Irma Thomas at the Ryman Auditorium on September 12.
